  "detailed_description": "<strong>SpaceKraft is a physics based spaceship simulation which you craft elements and explore the open world.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/8df187043f59b90c21a2e75f51497d54.poster.avif?t=1726593004\" width=600 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/8df187043f59b90c21a2e75f51497d54.webm?t=1726593004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/8df187043f59b90c21a2e75f51497d54.mp4?t=1726593004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Docking Arm and Crane Rope</strong><br>Spaceship has a docking arm to hold and move objects precisely and a crane rope in the back to lift objects from planet surfaces.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/97c00ef6110a36ed11779f93033d9054.poster.avif?t=1726593004\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/97c00ef6110a36ed11779f93033d9054.webm?t=1726593004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/97c00ef6110a36ed11779f93033d9054.mp4?t=1726593004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/43a04783c64ddfc5123107f040ef9fcd.poster.avif?t=1726593004\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/43a04783c64ddfc5123107f040ef9fcd.webm?t=1726593004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/43a04783c64ddfc5123107f040ef9fcd.mp4?t=1726593004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Crystals and Upgrades</strong><br>You can collect crystal energy to refuel, repair or upgrade your spaceship. Afterburner, armor, extra fuel tank, reinforced chassis and more...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/0d1039a38700ff344af38ee75ea71230.poster.avif?t=1726593004\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/0d1039a38700ff344af38ee75ea71230.webm?t=1726593004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/0d1039a38700ff344af38ee75ea71230.mp4?t=1726593004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/25241a9adfa0867c2d149ad0364b4472.poster.avif?t=1726593004\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/25241a9adfa0867c2d149ad0364b4472.webm?t=1726593004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/25241a9adfa0867c2d149ad0364b4472.mp4?t=1726593004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Run Generators</strong><br>In addition, crystals can be used to power generators that activate various machines or stations, which can be helpful in situations such as teleporting to another planet or sending an emergency signal for assistance.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/f90450c3e8a497e7dce3e733d15b5b23.poster.avif?t=1726593004\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/f90450c3e8a497e7dce3e733d15b5b23.webm?t=1726593004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/f90450c3e8a497e7dce3e733d15b5b23.mp4?t=1726593004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/e266b94b6756a3050681eaa43aed29bb.poster.avif?t=1726593004\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/e266b94b6756a3050681eaa43aed29bb.webm?t=1726593004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/e266b94b6756a3050681eaa43aed29bb.mp4?t=1726593004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><br><strong>Planets</strong><br>As you explore new planets, you can discover more resources to gather. Craft further elements to repair facilities. Each planet has its own unique features.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/7961c0db0b26fd90342ef748abec89b8.poster.avif?t=1726593004\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/7961c0db0b26fd90342ef748abec89b8.webm?t=1726593004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/7961c0db0b26fd90342ef748abec89b8.mp4?t=1726593004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/0ea99c3ded29febc24cc0f033dfa8a62.poster.avif?t=1726593004\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/0ea99c3ded29febc24cc0f033dfa8a62.webm?t=1726593004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/0ea99c3ded29febc24cc0f033dfa8a62.mp4?t=1726593004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Story</strong><br>Tom, our hero, finds himself abducted into an unknown universe where he must navigate through the strange new world, uncover the secrets of his abduction, and ultimately find a way back home to planet Earth.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/5131e87687d26a9a40822b35aaa24df2.poster.avif?t=1726593004\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/5131e87687d26a9a40822b35aaa24df2.webm?t=1726593004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703020/extras/5131e87687d26a9a40822b35aaa24df2.mp4?t=1726593004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
